  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetics and Safety of Solithromycin in Adolescents and Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Open-label, Multi-center Study to Determine the Pharmacokinetics and Safety of Solithromycin as Add-on Therapy in Adolescents and Children With Suspected or Confirmed Bacterial Infection</official_title>
